text.tspan: 32 registers. Register 0 is hardwired to 0, reading always returns 0 and writing has no effect.
i_rs1 and i_rs2 select which register to connect to o_reg1 and o_reg2.
i_rd selects which register to use as the destination. On the clock positive edge, when i_ce is HIGH
i_value is latched into the destination register.
